node.text: Senior Frontend Developer and Udemy instructor Ohans Emmanuel shares his advice for people learning how to code.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Udemy on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How to become a web designer'.

node.text:
With outdated information floating around the internet, it can be tough to figure out what it takes to become a web designer. 

#WebDesign expert and Udemy instructor Vako Shvili shares a comprehensive guide on our blog with everything you need to know about breaking into a career in web design. Link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Udemy on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'The Do's and Dont's of Zoom Communication "Being comfortable on camera is a skill! Identify any specific areas of struggle and look for practical adjustments to improve the way you look and feel." Alexa Fischer Udemy Confidence and Communication Instructor'.

node.text:
Let’s get real. #Zoom life is hard and knowing what to do - and what not to do - can be a lot. 

Udemy instructor Alexa Fischer shares the do’s and don’ts of video conferencing in our monthly skills index. Read up via the link in bio.
